course_title: Women's Health/Gender-Related NP Practicum V: Practice Integration
course_description: This fifth and final clinical course fully integrates the delivery of health care to the WHGRNP patient with policy and change. Emphasis is on transformation related to the delivery of sexual and reproductive health care.
prerequisites: NRSG 829D and NRSG 830D as prerequisites, NRSG 831D as co-requisite, or equivalent transfer credit.
